    <summary>
      <span data-ttu-id="a954b-101">为不能转换为输出字节序列的输入字符提供一个称为“回退”的失败处理机制。</span>
      <span class="sxs-lookup">
        <span data-stu-id="a954b-101">Provides a failure-handling mechanism, called a fallback, for an input character that cannot be converted to an output byte sequence.</span>
      </span>
      <span data-ttu-id="a954b-102">如果输入字符无法转换为输出字节序列，则回退引发异常。</span>
      <span class="sxs-lookup">
        <span data-stu-id="a954b-102">The fallback throws an exception if an input character cannot be converted to an output byte sequence.</span>
      </span>
